# pocket-md

============================================================
Pocket Molecular Dynamics for ARGON -- Serial/OpenMP VERSION
============================================================

Authors:  Ivan Korotkin, Sergey Karabasov
Date:     07/08/2017

Contacts: ivan.korotkin@gmail.com

============================================================


Features:

- Compact plain C code
- Tested for more than 10 000 000 Argon atoms
- OpenMP support
- Grid (Cell) neighbour search algorithm
- List-based neighbour search algorithm (faster but demands more memory)
- Berendsen thermostat
- Supports GROMACS GRO and XTC output formats for trajectories -- both suitable for visualisation in VMD


Use "help" option to get full list of supported options


